264
01:06:08.800 --> 01:06:11.680
If we're going to beat this thing. we need those pages.

265
01:06:15.800 --> 01:06:20.000
Then let's head down into that cellar and carve ourselves a witch.

266
01:07:08.800 --> 01:07:10.680
Groovy.

267
01:07:54.800 --> 01:07:56.680
Those pages are down there somewhere.

268
01:11:00.800 --> 01:11:04.800
"Nos veratos alamemnon conda."

269
01:12:00.800 --> 01:12:01.800
Let's go.

270
01:12:34.880 --> 01:12:36.800
I'll swallow your soul. I'll swallow your soul.

271
01:13:29.880 --> 01:13:31.800
Hey! I'll swallow your soul! I'll swallow your soul!

272
01:13:34.880 --> 01:13:36.800
Swallow this.

273
01:15:07.880 --> 01:15:09.880
I only completed the first of the passages

274
01:15:10.880 --> 01:15:12.800
and that was to make the Evil a thing of the flesh!

275
01:15:20.880 --> 01:15:22.800
Finish it!

276
01:15:23.880 --> 01:15:25.800
There's still the second passage.

277
01:15:30.880 --> 01:15:30.880
The one-

278
01:15:30.880 --> 01:15:33.000
the one to open the rift and send the Evil back!

279
01:15:33.880 --> 01:15:36.800
Well start reciting it! Now!

280
01:15:49.880 --> 01:15:51.800
Don't look Annie! Finish the passages!
Get rid of it!

281
01:16:13.880 --> 01:16:15.800
No!!!

282
01:17:11.880 --> 01:17:13.800
We've won. We've won. Victory is ours.

283
01:17:46.880 --> 01:17:48.880
You did it kid.

284
01:18:23.000 --> 01:18:25.000
By God... No!!!! For God's sake!

285
01:18:25.000 --> 01:18:26.880
How do you stop it?

286
01:19:45.000 --> 01:19:46.880
Slay the beast. It is a deadite!

287
01:19:47.880 --> 01:19:49.880
Run! Back to the castle!

288
01:20:26.000 --> 01:20:27.880
Hail he who has come from the skies

289
01:20:28.880 --> 01:20:30.880
to deliver us from the terrors of the deadites!

290
01:20:33.000 --> 01:20:34.880
Hail! Hail! Hail!

291
01:20:38.000 --> 01:20:39.880
No! No!! No!!! No!!!!!!
